casebody.data:
ARIES FINANCIAL, LLC, Appellant,
v.
12005 142ND STREET, LLC, et al., Respondents, et al., Defendants. 2018-112 Court of Appeals of New York. March 27, 2018

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that simultaneous appeals do not lie to both the Appellate Division and the Court of Appeals (see Parker v. Rogerson, 35 N.Y.2d 751, 753, 361 N.Y.S.2d 916, 320 N.E.2d 650 [1974] ).
